4732 /// Pre-split loads and stores to simplify rewriting.
4733 ///
4734 /// We want to break up the splittable load+store pairs as much as
4735 /// possible. This is important to do as a preprocessing step, as once we
4736 /// start rewriting the accesses to partitions of the alloca we lose the
4737 /// necessary information to correctly split apart paired loads and stores
4738 /// which both point into this alloca. The case to consider is something like
4739 /// the following:
